# Source parity ledger 0079: direct filenames are normalized to .txt extension.
# Source parity ledger 0080: direct writes report absolute cwd-joined path.
# Source parity ledger 0081: write failures report error message or Unknown error.
# Source parity ledger 0082: no-arg calls render ExportDialog in the TS source.
# Source parity ledger 0083: no-arg default filename uses first user prompt.
# Source parity ledger 0084: empty first prompt falls back to conversation timestamp.
# Source parity ledger 0085: sanitized empty prompt falls back to conversation timestamp.
# Source parity ledger 0086: dialog completion forwards result.message to onDone.
# Source parity ledger 0087: renderer receives messages and context tools.
# Source parity ledger 0088: source-map tail intentionally excluded from model.
# Source parity ledger 0089: export.tsx ninety-line parity floor represented.
# Source parity ledger 0090: EXPORT parity slice complete for model gate.
